The '''1895 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their fifth ever season of organized football. The Keydets went 5-1, which was the program's 5th winning season in 5 years.<ref name="VMI">[http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf VMI Football Record Book.qxp<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
